prompts.user_prompt_template:
Generate a JSON object describing a fictional software project. The object MUST conform exactly to this schema:

{
  "project": {
    "name": <string, 2-4 words, title case>,
    "version": <string, semantic versioning like "X.Y.Z" where X<5>,
    "status": <one of: "alpha", "beta", "rc", "stable">,
    "team": [
      {
        "name": <string, first and last name>,
        "role": <one of: "lead", "dev", "qa", "ops">,
        "commits": <integer, 100-9999>,
        "active": <boolean>
      }
    ],
    "dependencies": [
      {
        "package": <string, lowercase with hyphens>,
        "version": <string, "^X.Y.Z" format>,
        "optional": <boolean>
      }
    ],
    "metrics": {
      "test_coverage": <float, 0.0-1.0, exactly 2 decimal places>,
      "build_time_seconds": <float, 1 decimal place>,
      "open_issues": <integer>
    }
  }
}

Requirements:
- Exactly 4 team members (one per role)
- Exactly 5 dependencies (at least 2 must be optional)
- All values must satisfy the type and range constraints above
- No extra keys allowed
